Assignment 3: Drawing a Scene in 3D
Domenic Murtari (domenic.murtari@gmail.com)
Time taken to complete: ~4 hours

The scene starts out being rendered at 5 degrees elevation to allow the 
ground to be shown. 

Arrow keys used to rotate the scene
'a' to toggle axes
's' to toggle smoke animation
0 to reset view
Esc to exit